caption: In a modern office space, a black desk holds a black computer tower with a silver front panel, accompanied by a black flat-panel monitor above it. Nearby, a light gray file cabinet stands with the black computer tower on its right side, while a flat-screen monitor is positioned close by. Adjacent to the file cabinet, a dark backpack rests, and a shelf with various items is nearby. On the floor, a black shoe is visible, along with three brown cardboard boxes. One box is placed slightly higher on the shelf. Another area features a slim desk with a modern flat-screen monitor, a black keyboard, and a glossy black circular mouse. Positioned above the desk is a cream-colored corded telephone with an elongated receiver. Not far away, a metallic multi-tiered shelf holds a wide-brimmed brown hat, a rectangular brown cardboard box, and a green and white illustrated box. Additionally, a white paper sheet is placed on the desk, and two brown cardboard boxes are on the floor near a dark backpack.
